statements: UPSERT INTO car_details (car_id, make, model, year, color) VALUES (1, 'Toyota', 'Camry', 2022, 'Red')
UPSERT INTO car_details (car_id, make, model, year, color) VALUES (2, 'Honda', 'Accord', 2021, 'Blue')
UPSERT INTO car_details (car_id, make, model, year, color) VALUES (3, 'Ford', 'Mustang', 2020, 'Black')
UPSERT INTO vehicles (vehicle_id, make, model, year) VALUES (1, 'Toyota', 'Corolla', 2021) ON CONFLICT (vehicle_id) DO UPDATE SET make = 'Toyota', model = 'Corolla', year = 2021
UPSERT INTO vehicles (vehicle_id, make, model, year) VALUES (2, 'Honda', 'Accord', 2020) ON CONFLICT (vehicle_id) DO UPDATE SET make = 'Honda', model = 'Accord', year = 2020
UPSERT INTO owners (owner_id, vehicle_id, name, address) VALUES (1, 1, 'Alice', '123 Main St') ON CONFLICT (owner_id) DO UPDATE SET vehicle_id = 1, name = 'Alice', address = '123 Main St'
UPSERT INTO Car (id, make, model, year) VALUES (1, 'Toyota', 'Camry', 2022)
UPSERT INTO Manufacturer (id, name, country) VALUES (1, 'Toyota Motor Corporation', 'Japan')
UPSERT INTO Dealership (id, name, location, manufacturer_id) VALUES (1, 'Toyota Dealership', 'Tokyo', 1)
UPSERT INTO Cars (car_id, car_make, car_model, year, color) VALUES (1, 'Toyota', 'Camry', 2021, 'Red') ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE car_make='Toyota', car_model='Camry', year=2021, color='Red'
UPSERT INTO Owners (owner_id, owner_name, contact_number) VALUES (1, 'John Doe', '123-456-7890') ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE owner_name='John Doe', contact_number='123-456-7890'
UPSERT INTO Services (service_id, car_id, service_type, date, cost) VALUES (1, 1, 'Oil Change', '2021-10-15', 50.00) ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE service_type='Oil Change', date='2021-10-15', cost=50.00
INSERT INTO car (id, brand, model) VALUES (1, 'Toyota', 'Corolla') ON CONFLICT (id) DO UPDATE SET brand = excluded.brand, model = excluded.model
INSERT INTO engine (id, car_id, type, hp) VALUES (1, 1, 'V8', 400) ON CONFLICT (id) DO UPDATE SET car_id = excluded.car_id, type = excluded.type, hp = excluded.hp
INSERT INTO chassis (id, car_id, material, color) VALUES (1, 1, 'Aluminum', 'Silver') ON CONFLICT (id) DO UPDATE SET car_id = excluded.car_id, material = excluded.material, color = excluded.color
